17:["$","section","Profiles & Applications",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-4 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"h-1 w-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900","children":"Profiles & Applications"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/70 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-8","children":["$","$L12",null,{"type":"single","collapsible":true,"className":"w-full","children":[["$","$L13","0",{"value":"Profiles & Applications-0","children":[["$","$L14",null,{"className":"text-left text-gray-800 hover:no-underline","children":"Can I upload my CV to JOBR?"}],["$","$L15",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed text-gray-600","children":"Yes. You can upload your CV in PDF, DOC, or DOCX format through your profile dashboard. We recommend keeping your CV updated with your latest qualifications, work experience, and skills. A well-maintained CV on JOBR makes it easier for employers to find you and for you to apply to listings quickly. You can also set your profile to \"Open to Opportunities\" to increase your visibility to recruiters."}]]}],["$","$L13","1",{"value":"Profiles & Applications-1","children":[["$","$L14",null,{"className":"text-left text-gray-800 hover:no-underline","children":"How do I track my job applications?"}],["$","$L15",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed text-gray-600","children":"All your job applications are tracked in your profile dashboard under \"My Applications.\" Here you can see the status of each application (submitted, viewed, shortlisted, or rejected), the date you applied, and the job details. If an employer responds, you'll receive an email notification and can continue the conversation through our messaging system."}]]}]]}]}]]}]
